content: Once you've grabbed the Wisp, go in the opposite direction and past the Revenant Archer. On the other side of the underpass, you'll walk straight into another round of fighting. This time, you'll find the Revenants fighting Bull Sergeants.

This is an excerpt from the file 'Woods_of_Ember_Walkthrough.md', within the main section titled 'Woods of Ember Walkthrough', specifically from the subsection 'Ashen Pass I'.
The content is as follows:
Once you've grabbed the Wisp, go in the opposite direction and past the Revenant Archer. On the other side of the underpass, you'll walk straight into another round of fighting. This time, you'll find the Revenants fighting Bull Sergeants.
